      "content": "it doesn't feel like something i can \"reclaim\" though. that person is just... extinct. it's not like i lost a part of myself, it's like the real me is gone and this thing that's left is just a placeholder. a hollow thing that's just taking up space and consuming resources. it feels more like a burden than a life.",
